title: That's What Trends Are For 12/17: Deb Haaland, NBA, Roku, Snowblower, Tom Cruise
itunes:title: That's What Trends Are For 12/17: Deb Haaland, NBA, Roku, Snowblower, Tom Cruise
description:
On this edition of That's What Trends Are For Jack and Miles discuss Biden tapping Deb Haaland to be the first Native American Secretary of the Interior, the boys discuss the best NBA teams this season, HBO Max is now on Roku, Snowblowers are needed to help the people on the east coast, and Tom Cruise had ANOTHER flip out on the set of Mission Impossible.
